Package: scenesetr
Type: Package
Title: Construct and Render Interactive 3-Dimensional Scenes
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-11-22
Description: Interactively explore and animate custom 3-D scenes. Define behaviours of lights, cameras and objects in response to key inputs and each other, and record scenes as they pan out in real time. For a complete list of functions, use `help(package = "scenesetr")`.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
